  "system": {
    "description": "<p><span ><strong >Cantrip Passive:</strong> You deal +1 damage against creatures that are <strong >@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.x06moaa9pWzbdrxB.JournalEntryPage.610e6b3221204f0a]{Impaired}</strong>.</span></p><p ><span > </span></p><p ><span >You can produce 1 of the following effects:</span></p><p ><span ><strong >Spell Attack:</strong> You can make a <strong >Spell Check </strong>against the <strong >PD</strong> of a target within range.<br ><strong >Hit:</strong> The target takes 2 Poison damage.</span></p><p></p><p><span ><strong><span >Action Point Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><ul><li><p><strong>Damage: (1 AP)</strong> You deal +1 <span >Poison </span>damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Range: (1 AP)</strong> You increase the range by +5 Spaces.</p></li><li><p><span ><strong >Sicken</strong></span><strong>: (1 AP)</strong> <span >The target makes a <strong >Physical Save</strong></span>. <span ><strong >Failure:</strong></span> Target becomes <span ><strong >@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.x06moaa9pWzbdrxB.JournalEntryPage.610e6b3221204f0a]{Impaired}</strong><strong > </strong></span>for 1 minute. A creature can spend <span ><strong >1 AP</strong></span> to make a <span ><strong >DC 10</strong></span> <span ><strong >Medicine Check </strong></span>on itself or another creature within 1 Space to end the condition early.</p></li></ul>",
